epic.network

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • epic.network.Location

  • public class Location
extends Object
    Class to represent locations, using lat/long, northing/easting, or x/y, with an optional name field. provides methods to calculate distances between location also.
    Version:
    10 June 2014
    Author:
    slycett
